Note:
Runa Security Library: Performance Benchmarking Module

Production-grade benchmarking suite for security operations with comprehensive
performance analysis, profiling, and optimization recommendations. Surpasses
enterprise security benchmarking frameworks with advanced metrics collection,
statistical analysis, and automated performance regression detection.

Features:
- Comprehensive security operation benchmarking
- Real-time performance monitoring and profiling
- Statistical analysis with confidence intervals
- Automated performance regression detection
- Resource utilization tracking (CPU, memory, I/O)
- Load testing and stress testing capabilities
- Performance optimization recommendations
- Competitive analysis against industry standards
- Integration with APM and monitoring systems
:End Note

Import "datetime/datetime" as DateTime
Import "../../collections" as Collections
Import "math/core" as Math
Import "security/primitives/audit" as Audit
Import "security/primitives/permissions" as Permissions
Import "security/primitives/sandbox" as Sandbox
Import "security/verification/core" as Verification

Note: Core benchmarking data structures
Type called "BenchmarkSuite":
    suite_id as String
    name as String
    description as String
    benchmarks as List[SecurityBenchmark]
    configuration as BenchmarkConfig
    results as List[BenchmarkResult]
    statistics as BenchmarkStatistics
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type called "SecurityBenchmark":
    benchmark_id as String
    name as String
    category as BenchmarkCategory
    operation as SecurityOperation
    parameters as BenchmarkParameters
    expected_performance as PerformanceThreshold
    enabled as Boolean
    priority as BenchmarkPriority

Type BenchmarkCategory is:
    | Authentication
    | Authorization
    | Cryptography
    | AuditLogging
    | Sandboxing
    | Verification
    | NetworkSecurity
    | DataProtection
    | ComplianceChecking
    | ThreatDetection

Type called "SecurityOperation":
    operation_type as OperationType
    function_name as String
    input_data as Any
    setup_code as Optional[String]
    cleanup_code as Optional[String]
    validation_code as Optional[String]

Type OperationType is:
    | FunctionCall
    | ProcessExecution
    | SystemCall
    | NetworkOperation
    | DatabaseOperation
    | FileSystemOperation
    | CryptographicOperation
    | ComplianceCheck

Type called "BenchmarkParameters":
