Note: Load testing and stress testing capabilities
Process called "create_load_test_suite" that takes name as String and concurrent_users as Integer and duration_seconds as Integer returns LoadTestSuite:
    Let suite_id be generate_benchmark_id with prefix as "LOAD"
    Return LoadTestSuite with:
        suite_id as suite_id
        name as name
        concurrent_users as concurrent_users
        duration_seconds as duration_seconds
        ramp_up_seconds as duration_seconds / 10
        scenarios as list containing
        configuration as create_default_load_test_config()
        results as None
        status as NotStarted

