Type BottleneckType is:
    | CPU
    | Memory
    | DiskIO
    | NetworkIO
    | Database
    | Application

Type BottleneckSeverity is:
    | Critical
    | High
    | Medium
    | Low

Process called "execute_load_test" that takes load_test as LoadTestSuite returns LoadTestResults:
    Set load_test.status to Running
    Let test_start be DateTime.now()
    Let user_threads be create_virtual_users with count as load_test.concurrent_users and scenarios as load_test.scenarios
    Let results_collector be create_results_collector()
    start_real_time_monitoring with collector as results_collector
    execute_ramp_up_phase with threads as user_threads and ramp_up_seconds as load_test.ramp_up_seconds
    execute_steady_state_phase with threads as user_threads and duration_seconds as load_test.duration_seconds and collector as results_collector
    execute_ramp_down_phase with threads as user_threads
    stop_real_time_monitoring with collector as results_collector
    Let test_end be DateTime.now()
    Let results be aggregate_load_test_results with collector as results_collector and duration as DateTime.difference_seconds with start as test_start and end as test_end
    Set load_test.status to Completed
    Set load_test.results to results
    Return results

Note: Utility and helper functions
Process called "generate_benchmark_id" that takes prefix as String returns String:
    Let timestamp be DateTime.now_milliseconds()
    Let random_part be Math.random_int with min as 1000 and max as 9999
    Return String.concat with parts as list containing prefix, "-", timestamp, "-", random_part

Process called "generate_execution_id" returns String:
    Return generate_benchmark_id with prefix as "EXEC"

Process called "create_sample_audit_entry" returns Audit.AuditEntry:
    Let actor be Audit.Actor with:
        actor_id as "benchmark-user"
        actor_type as Audit.Human
        name as "Benchmark User"
        roles as list containing "tester"
        session_id as "benchmark-session"
        source_ip as "127.0.0.1"
        user_agent as "runa-benchmark-suite"
    Return Audit.create_audit_entry with
        event_type as Audit.Authentication
